      Create a new trust. Special operation. Participating HSMs and operators are given at start. Random participating HSM is used.
      Parameters:
      hmsIdsList - a list of the HSMs public keys to add to the trust.
      operatorPublicKeyIndexList - a list of the operator public keys.
      Returns:
      true if success else false.

      public boolean operatorSignTrust(int trustId, PrivateKey privateKey)

      true if success else false.
